I"ä<p>There are a lot of them out there, as most ESPs come with a WYSIWYG editor built in. A lot of email folks are partial to Adobe Dreamweaver for its WYSIWYG editor. They vary in quality and oftentimes produce bloated, unoptimized code. Use with care.</p>

